The paper deals with security and privacy challenges in the V2G infrastructure, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The proposed solution involves the use of blockchain technology, which is a popular topic in the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also deals with energy trading and communication between entities, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
